### Health
GET http://localhost:3000/api/health

### Track morning habit
POST http://localhost:3000/api/habits/track
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "alex",
  "timestamp": "2026-03-13T08:00:00+05:30",
  "location": "home",
  "destination": "office",
  "action": "leave for work",
  "notes": "weekday commute",
  "source": "watch"
}

### Register watch hook
POST http://localhost:3000/api/devices/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "alex",
  "deviceType": "watch",
  "platform": "wearos",
  "hookUrl": "https://example.com/watch-hook",
  "pushToken": "watch-token-001",
  "enabled": true
}

### Register mobile hook
POST http://localhost:3000/api/devices/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "alex",
  "deviceType": "mobile",
  "platform": "android",
  "hookUrl": "https://example.com/mobile-hook",
  "pushToken": "mobile-token-001",
  "enabled": true
}

### Get reminder
GET http://localhost:3000/api/reminders?userId=alex&timestamp=2026-03-13T08:10:00%2B05:30&currentLocation=home

### Chat
POST http://localhost:3000/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "alex",
  "timestamp": "2026-03-13T08:10:00+05:30",
  "currentLocation": "home",
  "message": "What should I do now?"
}

### Pending notifications for watch
GET http://localhost:3000/api/notifications/pending?userId=alex&deviceType=watch

### Acknowledge notification
POST http://localhost:3000/api/notifications/ack
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "notificationId": 1,
  "userId": "alex",
  "status": "ACKNOWLEDGED",
  "responseOption": "remind_now"
}

### Manually run reminder cron (optional local test)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/cron/dispatch-reminders
Authorization: Bearer {{CRON_SECRET}}
